[normal]I am aged 70, have cycled for independence as a child, and for transport, exercise &amp; fun ever since. Recently retired and involved with 
[normal]Transition To
[normal]w
[normal]n Totnes
[normal] since 
[normal]the 
[normal]start
[normal] of
[normal] 
[normal]what is
[normal] now 
[normal]a 
[normal]world-wide 
[normal]movement, I started the Cycling Group for fun
[normal],
[normal] and to work on Sustainable Transport for access to the surrounding villages and within the town.
