[normal]FINDINGS
[normal]Implementation of the Strategy
[normal]“
[normal]In the first four years, the Strategy has been implemented with energy and 
[normal]enthusiasm in an atmosphere of cooperation and consensus among those 
[normal]involved. Teenage pr
[normal]egnancy has been taken seriously enough to secure 
[normal]engagement of senior policy makers and dedicated funding, resulting in rapid
[normal]and efficient action. Joint working has been achieved even in areas where it
[normal]has not previously been evident. The local teenage 
[normal]pregnancy coordinator
[normal]has been the lynchpin of implementation; their status in the community, their
[normal]professional experience and the support they have received have been key
[normal]to the success of their role.
[normal]”
